longBusinessSummary: NHMD Holdings, Inc. engages in the Bitcoin mining activities. It owns and operates application-specific integrated circuit computers designed for cryptocurrency mining. The company was formerly known as Nate's Food Co. and changed its name to NHMD Holdings, Inc. in March 2022. NHMD Holdings, Inc. is headquartered in Huntington Beach, California.
